text:
Last year when I had to choose what I want study for this new year, I had no idea about what I would like to do. At the begining I was more focused about where I want to study rather that what I really want to do. All my education I was doing well in languages, so in a kind of ease I thougth about continue my graduate studies in this way. What I wanted for my future was to travel ( because it’s an habit un my family to travel a lot) so go to a language training will be a continuity to this idea.
In an other option I had obviously a « BTS TOURISME » but I wasn’t overjoyed about that.
The year passed and I discuss with my mom about what kind of studies she have done : she talk to me about a « BTS INFORMATION COMMUNICATION » at Rennes. She explain me what she had to do, show me some graphic project and I loved that.
When parcoursup opened I  didn’t find the BTS that she told me but there was an university degree in Information Communication. My sistre went already in Rennes 2 so I decided to show her and here I am.
 This webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a textbox. In other words , when focused on the text below, the page will record  each time you hit a key or select text with your mouse. All of thé data is stored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as a JSON file. More information about the motivation of this project and the format of the produced data are available here
